;
1. Twinned data refinement
 Scales: 0.841(3) 0.159(3)
2. Fixed Uiso
 At 1.2 times of:
  All C(H,H) groups, All N(H,H,H) groups
3. Restrained distances
 C2-C3
 1.54 with sigma of 0.02
4. Rigid bond restraints
 N1, C1, C2, C3, C4, N2
 with sigma for 1-2 distances of 0.01 and sigma for 1-3 distances of 0.01
5. Uiso/Uaniso restraints and constraints
N1 \\sim C1 \\sim C2 \\sim C3 \\sim C4 \\sim N2: within 2A with sigma of 0.04
and sigma for terminal atoms of 0.08
6.a Secondary CH2 refined with riding coordinates:
 C1(H1D,H1E), C4(H4A,H4B), C2(H2D,H2E), C3(H3A,H3B)
6.b Idealised Me refined as rotating group:
 N2(H2A,H2B,H2C), N1(H1A,H1B,H1C)
;
